{"text_id":123373,"tokens":["The"," paper"," \"","Efficient"," Summar","ization"," with"," Read","-","Again"," and"," Copy"," Mechanism","\""," addresses"," two"," major"," shortcomings"," in"," the"," current"," sequence","-","to","-","sequence"," prediction"," tasks"," using"," encoder","-","decoder"," models","."," These"," shortcomings"," include"," the"," sub","optimal"," representation"," of"," individual"," words"," by"," the"," encoder"," and"," the"," utilization"," of"," large"," vocab","ular","ies"," resulting"," in"," slow"," decoding"," times"," and"," large"," storage"," costs","."," ","\n","The"," paper"," presents"," a"," simple"," mechanism"," that"," addresses"," these"," shortcomings"," by"," first"," reading"," the"," input"," sequence"," before"," committing"," to"," a"," representation"," of"," each"," word"," and"," proposing"," a"," copy"," mechanism"," that"," is"," capable"," of"," exploiting"," small"," vocab","ular","ies"," and"," handling"," out","-","of","-","vocabulary"," words","."," The"," authors"," test"," their"," approach"," on"," the"," Gig","aw","ord"," dataset"," and"," D","UC"," competition",","," out","performing"," existing"," state","-","of","-","the","-","art"," models",".","\n","The"," major"," strength"," of"," this"," paper"," is"," its"," clever"," and"," well","-","presented"," solutions"," to"," existing"," shortcomings"," in"," the"," current"," approach"," to"," sequence","-","to","-","sequence"," prediction"," tasks","."," The"," paper"," introduces"," a"," simple"," yet"," effective"," mechanism"," for"," reading"," an"," input"," sequence"," before"," representing"," each"," word",","," which"," significantly"," improves"," the"," performance"," of"," the"," model","."," The"," authors"," have"," also"," proposed"," a"," copy"," mechanism",","," which"," is"," a"," very"," clever"," solution"," to"," handle"," out","-","of","-","vocabulary"," words",".","\n","One"," drawback"," of"," this"," paper"," is"," that"," the"," authors"," did"," not"," compare"," their"," approach"," with"," other"," state","-","of","-","the","-","art"," methods"," on"," a"," wider"," range"," of"," datasets","."," Moreover",","," although"," the"," authors"," present"," a"," simple"," copy"," mechanism",","," it"," is"," not"," clear"," from"," the"," results"," how"," effective"," this"," mechanism"," is"," in"," comparison"," to"," more"," complex"," alternative"," methods","."," The"," paper"," would"," have"," been"," stronger"," if"," the"," authors"," had"," provided"," more"," in","-","depth"," analysis"," of"," the"," mechanism","'","s"," effectiveness"," in"," different"," scenarios",".","\n","Overall",","," the"," paper"," \"","Efficient"," Summar","ization"," with"," Read","-","Again"," and"," Copy"," Mechanism","\""," presents"," an"," innovative"," approach"," for"," addressing"," existing"," shortcomings"," in"," sequence","-","to","-","sequence"," prediction"," tasks","."," Therefore",","," I"," would"," recommend"," this"," paper"," for"," publication"," with"," minor"," revisions",","," including"," providing"," more"," the"," in","-","depth"," analysis"," of"," the"," copy"," mechanism"," and"," comparing"," the"," proposed"," approach"," with"," other"," existing"," state","-","of","-","the","-","art"," methods","."],"sub_source":"peerread","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}